Package: ats-proxy-hardening
Version: 3.0-beta-1
Section: net
Priority: optional
Architecture: amd64
Depends: ats-core (>= 9.2.13), ufw, fail2ban, etckeeper
Maintainer: ATS Proxy Enterprise <proxy@tripersonale.org>
Homepage: https://github.com/tripersonale/ats-proxy-enterprise
Description: ATS Proxy Enterprise v3.0 hardening profile
 Systemd sandbox, UFW firewall rules, fail2ban auth failure detection,
 unattended-upgrades verification, etckeeper, health check cron, CVE helper.
 Applies only to the ATS proxy; can be used without the plugin package.
